    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it looks just as stunning as the day I first got it. It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, always garage-kept, and still has that 'brand new' sparkle inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that's practically perfect and ready for the road, this is definitely the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 46500.0,
