    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2005 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-precision 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the VANOS unit has been overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural weak point\u2014has been proactively reinforced. It retains its factory-spec variable M-differential lock and M-tuned suspension geometry, providing telepathic turn-in and exceptional lateral grip. The interior is an immaculate time capsule of Nappa leather and brushed aluminum. No deferred maintenance, no modifications, just pure, high-revving mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
