    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that has been maintained with obsessive care. This vehicle looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, completely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of pristine materials; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple with no signs of creasing, and the carpets are spotless. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the touch-sensitive climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented by a complete, chronological set of service records from the original dealership. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands the very best. Sale includes all original keys, factory manuals, and a custom-fit breathable car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
